abstract: Food and Drug Administration approves Fluac, first-of-a-kind seasonal flu vaccine to help protect vulnerable seniors; vaccine contains squalene, substance that boosts body's immune response.
lead_paragraph: Federal health officials have approved a first-of-a-kind flu vaccine that contains a booster to help protect seniors vulnerable to the virus.

headline.main: Flu Vaccine With Booster Gains F.D.A. Approval
headline.print_headline: Flu Vaccine With Booster Gains F.D.A. Approval
